Consider the following class:

```java
public class Temp
{
    private int val;

    public Temp(int val)
    {
        this.val = val;
    }

    public void adjust(int val)
    {
        val = val * 2;
        this.val = this.val + val;
    }

    public int getVal() { return val; }
}
```

What is printed by the following code?

```java
Temp t = new Temp(10);
t.adjust(3);
System.out.println(t.getVal());
```

